dc_title_s: Alternative Fuel Filling Stations: United States, Fall 2014
dc_description_s: This point dataset shows the locations of alternative fuel filling stations in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Fall Quarter update (Update 1017).This shapefile can be used to locate alternative fuel filling stations in the United States. point dataset shows the locations of oil seed processing plants in the United States for 2013. This layer is a part of a collection of GIS data containing renewable and electric energy information for the U.S., including data on transmission lines, power plants and electricity substations.
